        "# features\n",
        "X = df[[\"Molecular Weight\"]].values\n",
        "X = X.reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "X = np.hstack([np.ones_like(X), X])\n",
        "\n",
        "# ground truth\n",
        "Y = df[\"measured log solubility in mols per litre\"].values\n",
        "Y = Y.reshape(-1, 1)"
      ]
    },

        "## Analytical solution"

    },
    {

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 8,

        "id": "27e1e9b3-bfdd-469e-a582-cca65c58d3b6"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "theta = np.linalg.inv((X.T @ X)) @ (X.T @ Y)"
      ]
    },

        "print(f\"Loss: {loss}\")"

    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "919308fc",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "919308fc"
      },
      "source": [
        "## Gradient Descent"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "TECYsUDdcRdh",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "TECYsUDdcRdh"
      },
      "source": [
        "![Reference_Ch4_linear_regression_4.png](data:image/png;base64,)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 14,
      "id": "cde37cdb",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "cde37cdb"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "lr = 1e-6\n",
        "\n",
        "theta_list = []\n",
        "loss_list = []\n",
        "# theta = np.random.randn(2, 1).reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "theta = np.array([0, 0]).reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "n_epochs = 100\n",
        "\n",
        "for _ in range(n_epochs):\n",
        "    theta_list.append(copy.deepcopy(theta))\n",
        "    y_pred = X @ theta\n",
        "    loss = np.mean((y_pred - Y).reshape(-1)**2)\n",
        "    loss_list.append(loss)\n",
        "    grad = 2*X.T @ (X @ theta - Y) / Y.shape[0]\n",
        "    theta = theta - lr * grad"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 15,
      "id": "4574826f",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "4574826f",
        "outputId": "d4f0e1bf-5b7b-4ece-c4f5-caf97f032365"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Final loss: 2.6216033000052184\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "print(\"Final loss:\", loss_list[-1])"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",

        "plt.ylabel(\"Loss\")"
      ]

            "/tmp/ipython-input-4040914613.py:19: UserWarning: No artists with labels found to put in legend.  Note that artists whose label start with an underscore are ignored when legend() is called with no argument.\n",
            "  legend = plt.legend(loc=\"upper right\")\n"
          ]
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "image/png": "",
            "text/plain": [
              "<Figure size 500x500 with 1 Axes>"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "display_data"
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "f, ax = plt.subplots(1, 1, figsize=(5, 5))\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "ax.scatter(X[:, -1], Y.reshape(-1), \\\n",
        "            s=15, marker='o', \\\n",
        "            facecolors='none', edgecolor=\"blue\")\n",
        "\n",
        "min_X = np.min(X[:, -1])\n",
        "max_X = np.max(X[:, -1])\n",
        "x_line = np.linspace(np.floor(min_X), np.ceil(max_X), 100)\n",
        "x_line = x_line.reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "x_line = np.hstack([np.ones_like(x_line), x_line])\n",
        "\n",
        "line, = ax.plot([], [], color=\"orange\", label=\"\")\n",
        "\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel(\"Molecular Weight (Da.)\")\n",
        "ax.set_ylabel(\"log solubility (mol/L)\")\n",
        "\n",
        "legend = plt.legend(loc=\"upper right\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def animate(i):\n",
        "    y_pred_line = x_line @ theta_list[i]\n",
        "    line.set_data(x_line[:, -1], y_pred_line)\n",
        "    line.set_label(f\"Epoch: {i}\")\n",
        "    legend = plt.legend()\n",
        "    return line, legend\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "ani = animation.FuncAnimation(f, animate, repeat=True, frames=len(theta_list), interval=100, blit=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "writer = animation.PillowWriter(fps=10,\n",
        "                                metadata=dict(artist='Me'),\n",
        "                                bitrate=1800)\n",
        "ani.save(\"theta_iteration.gif\", writer=writer)"
      ]
    },

      "source": [
        "## Data Normalization in Gradient Descent"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "T_h8C_qbcXFo",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "T_h8C_qbcXFo"
      },
      "source": [
        "![Reference_Ch4_linear_regression_5.png](data:image/png;base64,)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "dzeqL6tlcc0S",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "dzeqL6tlcc0S"
      },
      "source": [
        "![Reference_Ch4_linear_regression_6.png](data:image/png;base64,)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 18,
      "id": "ebc0fc80",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ebc0fc80"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler\n",
        "\n",
        "scaler = StandardScaler()\n",
        "norm_mw = scaler.fit_transform(df[[\"Molecular Weight\"]].values)\n",
        "X = np.hstack([np.ones_like(norm_mw), norm_mw])"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 19,
      "id": "29c89721",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "29c89721"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "lr = 1e-1\n",
        "\n",
        "theta_list = []\n",
        "loss_list = []\n",
        "# theta = np.random.randn(2, 1).reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "theta = np.array([0, 0]).reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "n_epochs = 20\n",
        "\n",
        "for _ in range(n_epochs):\n",
        "    theta_list.append(copy.deepcopy(theta))\n",
        "    y_pred = X @ theta\n",
        "    loss = np.mean((y_pred - Y).reshape(-1)**2)\n",
        "    loss_list.append(loss)\n",
        "    grad = 2*X.T @ (X @ theta - Y) / Y.shape[0]\n",
        "    theta = theta - lr * grad"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 20,
      "id": "c7bd8016",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "c7bd8016",
        "outputId": "53a56dc2-2fb5-45a7-de0d-4ee5ea765bce"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Final loss: 2.593787495277282\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "print(\"Final loss:\", loss_list[-1])"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",

        "### Parameter Contour"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 22,
      "id": "1af77be8",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1af77be8"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def V(xx, yy):\n",
        "    losses = []\n",
        "    theta = np.hstack([xx.reshape(-1, 1), yy.reshape(-1, 1)])\n",
        "    for i in range(theta.shape[0]):\n",
        "        y_pred = X @ theta[i].reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "        loss = np.mean((y_pred - Y).reshape(-1)**2)\n",
        "        losses.append(loss)\n",
        "    return np.array(losses)\n",
        "\n",
        "# calculate contour\n",
        "t1 = np.arange(-6, 2, 1e-1)\n",
        "t2 = np.arange(-4, 4, 1e-1)\n",
        "xx, yy = np.meshgrid(t1, t2)\n",
        "z = V(xx.ravel(), yy.ravel()).reshape(len(t2), -1)"
      ]
    },

    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "dc20880b",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "dc20880b"
      },
      "source": [
        "## Stochastic Gradient Descent and Mini-batching"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "fZY67ujSchnk",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "fZY67ujSchnk"
      },
      "source": [
        "![Reference_Ch4_linear_regression_7.png](data:image/png;base64,)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 24,
      "id": "52c42cf9",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "52c42cf9"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "lr = 1e-1\n",
        "\n",
        "theta_list = []\n",
        "loss_list = []\n",
        "theta = np.array([0, 0]).reshape(-1, 1)\n",
        "n_epochs = 100\n",
        "batch_size = 32 # change the batch size here\n",
        "\n",
        "for _ in range(n_epochs):\n",
        "    indices = np.random.choice(X.shape[0], batch_size, replace=False)\n",
        "    theta_list.append(copy.deepcopy(theta))\n",
        "    y_pred = X[indices, :] @ theta\n",
        "    y_true = Y[indices]\n",
        "    loss = np.mean((y_pred - y_true).reshape(-1)**2)\n",
        "    loss_list.append(loss)\n",
        "    grad = 2*X[indices, :].T @ (y_pred - y_true) / len(indices)\n",
        "    theta = theta - lr * grad"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 25,
      "id": "61a60b20",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "61a60b20",
        "outputId": "f8c4ee3f-40e3-410b-8d67-1e9e01ef4a5a"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Final loss: 2.8454754567289027\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "print(\"Final loss:\", pd.Series(loss_list).rolling(5).mean().iloc[-1])"
      ]
    },
    {
